imdb.plot outline: Sponsored is the scripted series created by Cara Santana, that discovers the sordid underbelly of social media's "Instagram models" and their male sponsors. From yachts, vacations, expensive accessories and their million plus social media pages, the truth about what they are selling and who they are selling it to, uncovers a modern day prostitution ring. Sex sells and it's now on our feeds.
